        <div class="content">
            <!-- Section 1: 概念入门 -->
            <section id="intro" class="section">
                <h2 class="section-title"><span class="icon">📖</span> 01 概念入门 - TVM是什么？</h2>

                <div class="concept-box">
                    <div class="english">Time Value of Money (TVM)</div>
                    <div class="chinese"><strong>货币时间价值</strong> - 指货币随着时间的推移而发生的增值。简单来说，今天的1元钱比明天的1元钱更有价值。</div>
                </div>

                <div class="subsection">
                    <h3 class="subsection-title">为什么要理解TVM？</h3>
                    <p>同学们，想象一下：</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>如果有人现在给你1000元，或者一年后给你1000元，你会选哪个？</li>
                        <li>显然，大多数人会选择<span class="highlight">现在拿到钱</span>！</li>
                    </ul>
                    <div class="note">
                        💡 这就是货币时间价值的核心思想：钱具有"时间属性"，越早拿到，价值越大。
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="subsection">
                    <h3 class="subsection-title">TVM的三大原因</h3>
                    <table>
                        <tr>
                            <th>English</th>
                            <th>中文解析</th>
                            <th>通俗解释</th>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>Opportunity Cost</td>
                            <td><strong>机会成本</strong></td>
                            <td>今天拿到的钱可以投资赚钱，产生收益</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>Inflation Risk</td>
                            <td><strong>通货膨胀风险</strong></td>
                            <td>今天的100元能买到的东西，一年后可能只能买到90元的东西</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>Uncertainty Risk</td>
                            <td><strong>不确定性风险</strong></td>
                            <td>今天到手的是确定的，未来拿到的是不确定的（可能会违约）</td>
                        </tr>
                    </table>
                </div>

                <div class="subsection">
                    <h3 class="subsection-title">核心符号表</h3>
                    <table>
                        <tr>
                            <th>符号</th>
                            <th>英文全称</th>
                            <th>中文含义</th>
                            <th>记忆口诀</th>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td><strong>PV</strong></td>
                            <td>Present Value</td>
                            <td>现值 / 当前价值</td>
                            <td>P = Present = 现在</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td><strong>FV</strong></td>
                            <td>Future Value</td>
                            <td>终值 / 未来价值</td>
                            <td>F = Future = 未来</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td><strong>r</strong></td>
                            <td>Interest Rate / Discount Rate</td>
                            <td>利率 / 折现率</td>
                            <td>r = rate = 利率</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td><strong>n</strong></td>
                            <td>Number of Periods</td>
                            <td>期数</td>
                            <td>n = number = 数量</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td><strong>PMT</strong></td>
                            <td>Payment</td>
                            <td>每期支付金额</td>
                            <td>PMT = Payment = 支付</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td><strong>t</strong></td>
                            <td>Time</td>
                            <td>时间（年）</td>
                            <td>t = time = 时间</td>
                        </tr>
                    </table>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- Section 2: 四大公式 -->
            <section id="formulas" class="section">
                <h2 class="section-title"><span class="icon">📐</span> 02 TVM四大公式（必背！）</h2>

                <div class="summary-box">
                    <h3>💪 今日必会：TVM四大公式能默写+熟练应用</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li>FV = PV × (1 + r)<sup>n</sup> ← 复利终值</li>
                        <li>PV = FV / (1 + r)<sup>n</sup> ← 复利现值</li>
                        <li>FV<sub>annuity</sub> = PMT × [(1 + r)<sup>n</sup> - 1] / r ← 年金终值</li>
                        <li>PV<sub>annuity</sub> = PMT × [1 - (1 + r)<sup>-n</sup>] / r ← 年金现值</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="formula-card">
                    <h4><span class="number">1</span> Future Value (FV) - 终值公式</h4>
                    <div class="formula-box">
                        <div class="formula">FV = PV × (1 + r)<sup>n</sup></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="concept-box">
                        <div class="english">The process of calculating the future value of an investment based on the assumption of compound interest.</div>
                        <div class="chinese"><strong>复利终值</strong>：已知现在的金额，计算未来某个时点的价值。这就是"让钱生钱"的过程！</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="example-box">
                        <div class="title">📘 例题讲解</div>
                        <p><strong>题目：</strong>假设你今天存入银行10,000元，年利率为5%，复利计算，3年后账户里有多少钱？</p>
                        <p><strong>解题：</strong></p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>PV = 10,000元（现在的本金）</li>
                            <li>r = 5% = 0.05</li>
                            <li>n = 3年</li>
                        </ul>
                        <p>FV = 10,000 × (1 + 0.05)<sup>3</sup> = 10,000 × 1.1576 = <strong>11,576.25元</strong></p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="pitfall-box">
                        <div class="title">防坑攻略</div>
                        <p><strong>English:</strong> Always convert the percentage rate to decimal form before using it in the formula.</p>
                        <p><strong>中文:</strong> 千万不要直接把5%代入公式！要先转换成小数0.05再计算！</p>
                        <p>❌ 错误：FV = 10000 × (1 + 5)<sup>3</sup></p>
                        <p>✅ 正确：FV = 10000 × (1 + 0.05)<sup>3</sup></p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="formula-card">
                    <h4><span class="number">2</span> Present Value (PV) - 现值公式</h4>
                    <div class="formula-box">
                        <div class="formula">PV = FV / (1 + r)<sup>n</sup></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="concept-box">
                        <div class="english">The process of determining the current worth of a future sum of money or stream of cash flows.</div>
                        <div class="chinese"><strong>复利现值</strong>：已知未来的金额，计算其现在的价值。这就是"折现"的过程，把未来的钱"打折"回现在！</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="example-box">
                        <div class="title">📘 例题讲解</div>
                        <p><strong>题目：</strong>你将在3年后收到20,000元，如果年折现率是6%，这笔钱的现值是多少？</p>
                        <p><strong>解题：</strong></p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>FV = 20,000元（未来的金额）</li>
                            <li>r = 6% = 0.06</li>
                            <li>n = 3年</li>
                        </ul>
                        <p>PV = 20,000 / (1 + 0.06)<sup>3</sup> = 20,000 / 1.191 = <strong>16,792.39元</strong></p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="memory-tip">
                        <div class="title">记忆技巧</div>
                        <p>现值公式其实就是终值公式的<strong>倒数</strong>！记住PV就是FV除以那个系数就行！</p>
                        <p>口诀："终往现，除系数；现往终，乘系数"</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="formula-card">
                    <h4><span class="number">3</span> Future Value of Annuity - 年金终值公式</h4>
                    <div class="formula-box">
                        <div class="formula">FV<sub>A</sub> = PMT × [(1 + r)<sup>n</sup> - 1] / r</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="concept-box">
                        <div class="english">An Annuity is a series of equal payments made at regular intervals. The future value of an annuity calculates the total value of these payments at a future date.</div>
                        <div class="chinese"><strong>年金终值</strong>：计算一系列定期等额支付在未来某个时点的总价值。比如每月存入固定金额，计算n年后总共能有多少钱。</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="concept-box">
                        <div class="english">Ordinary Annuity vs. Annuity Due</div>
                        <div class="chinese">
                            <strong>普通年金：</strong>每期期末付款（最常见）<br>
                            <strong>预付年金：</strong>每期期初付款（多乘一个1+r）
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="example-box">
                        <div class="title">📘 例题讲解</div>
                        <p><strong>题目：</strong>你计划每年年末存入银行5,000元，年利率7%，连续存5年。5年后你账户里有多少钱？（普通年金）</p>
                        <p><strong>解题：</strong></p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>PMT = 5,000元（每年存入金额）</li>
                            <li>r = 7% = 0.07</li>
                            <li>n = 5年</li>
                        </ul>
                        <p>FV<sub>A</sub> = 5,000 × [(1 + 0.07)<sup>5</sup> - 1] / 0.07</p>
                        <p>FV<sub>A</sub> = 5,000 × [1.4026 - 1] / 0.07</p>
                        <p>FV<sub>A</sub> = 5,000 × 0.4026 / 0.07</p>
                        <p>FV<sub>A</sub> = 5,000 × 5.751 = <strong>28,754.94元</strong></p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="pitfall-box">
                        <div class="title">防坑攻略</div>
                        <p><strong>English:</strong> Be careful with the annuity type. For annuity due (beginning of period), multiply the result by (1 + r).</p>
                        <p><strong>中文:</strong> 注意区分普通年金和预付年金！</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>普通年金（期末付款）：直接用公式</li>
                            <li>预付年金（期初付款）：结果再 × (1+r)</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="formula-card">
                    <h4><span class="number">4</span> Present Value of Annuity - 年金现值公式</h4>
                    <div class="formula-box">
                        <div class="formula">PV<sub>A</sub> = PMT × [1 - (1 + r)<sup>-n</sup>] / r</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="concept-box">
                        <div class="english">The present value of an annuity calculates the current worth of a series of future equal payments.</div>
                        <div class="chinese"><strong>年金现值</strong>：计算一系列未来等额支付的当前总价值。比如计算每月还房贷的等额支付，折算成现在借了多少钱。</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="example-box">
                        <div class="title">📘 例题讲解</div>
                        <p><strong>题目：</strong>你打算购买一项年金，该年金将在未来10年内每年年末给你支付6,000元。如果年利率是8%，这个年金现在值多少钱？</p>
                        <p><strong>解题：</strong></p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>PMT = 6,000元（每年收到金额）</li>
                            <li>r = 8% = 0.08</li>
                            <li>n = 10年</li>
                        </ul>
                        <p>PV<sub>A</sub> = 6,000 × [1 - (1 + 0.08)<sup>-10</sup>] / 0.08</p>
                        <p>PV<sub>A</sub> = 6,000 × [1 - 0.4632] / 0.08</p>
                        <p>PV<sub>A</sub> = 6,000 × 0.5368 / 0.08</p>
                        <p>PV<sub>A</sub> = 6,000 × 6.710 = <strong>40,260.49元</strong></p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="memory-tip">
                        <div class="title">记忆技巧</div>
                        <p>年金现值公式和年金终值公式的关系：</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>终值：[(1+r)<sup>n</sup> - 1] / r ← 分子是1的n次幂减1</li>
                            <li>现值：[1 - (1+r)<sup>-n</sup>] / r ← 分子是1减去1的-n次幂</li>
                        </ul>
                        <p>口诀："终值减一在分子，现值一减负次幂"</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="subsection">
                    <h3 class="subsection-title">补充：永续年金</h3>
                    <div class="formula-box">
                        <div class="formula">PV<sub>perpetuity</sub> = PMT / r</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="concept-box">
                        <div class="english">A perpetuity is an annuity that has no end, or a stream of cash payments that continues forever.</div>
                        <div class="chinese"><strong>永续年金</strong>：永远持续下去的年金，没有到期日。比如优先股的股息通常被视为永续年金。</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- Section 3: 例题讲解 -->
            <section id="examples" class="section">
                <h2 class="section-title"><span class="icon">📝</span> 03 例题讲解</h2>

                <div class="exercise-box">
                    <h4 style="color: #9c27b0; margin-bottom: 15px;">例题 1：单笔投资的终值</h4>
                    <p class="question">如果你现在投资$15,000，年利率为6%，复利计算，4年后这笔投资将变成多少钱？</p>
                    <div class="answer-box">
                        <div class="correct">正确答案：$18,937.15</div>
                        <p><strong>解题步骤：</strong></p>
                        <ol>
                            <li>识别变量：PV = $15,000, r = 6% = 0.06, n = 4</li>
                            <li>选择公式：FV = PV × (1 + r)<sup>n</sup></li>
                            <li>代入计算：FV = 15,000 × (1 + 0.06)<sup>4</sup></li>
                            <li>FV = 15,000 × 1.2625 = $18,937.15</li>
                        </ol>
                    </div>
                    <div class="analysis-box">
                        <div class="title">归因分析</div>
                        <p>本题考查的是<strong>复利终值</strong>的计算。解题关键是：</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>✅ 正确识别PV（现值）为已知条件</li>
                            <li>✅ 正确将百分比利率转换为小数</li>
                            <li>✅ 注意是复利计算，不是单利</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="exercise-box">
                    <h4 style="color: #9c27b0; margin-bottom: 15px;">例题 2：未来金额的现值</h4>
                    <p class="question">你计划在5年后购买一辆价值$35,000的汽车。如果你现在投资一笔钱，年收益率为8%，你现在需要投资多少钱才能在5年后拥有$35,000？</p>
                    <div class="answer-box">
                        <div class="correct">正确答案：$23,820.48</div>
                        <p><strong>解题步骤：</strong></p>
                        <ol>
                            <li>识别变量：FV = $35,000, r = 8% = 0.08, n = 5</li>
                            <li>选择公式：PV = FV / (1 + r)<sup>n</sup></li>
                            <li>代入计算：PV = 35,000 / (1 + 0.08)<sup>5</sup></li>
                            <li>PV = 35,000 / 1.4693 = $23,820.48</li>
                        </ol>
                    </div>
                    <div class="analysis-box">
                        <div class="title">归因分析</div>
                        <p>本题考查的是<strong>折现计算</strong>（求现值）。注意：</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>✅ 这是"逆运算"，从未来推回现在</li>
                            <li>✅ 折现率越高，现值越低（因为除数越大）</li>
                            <li>✅ 时间越长，现值越低（因为分母指数越大）</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="exercise-box">
                    <h4 style="color: #9c27b0; margin-bottom: 15px;">例题 3：退休储蓄计划</h4>
                    <p class="question">小王计划每年年末存入$8,000到退休基金，年利率为7%，计划工作30年后退休。退休时账户里会有多少钱？</p>
                    <div class="answer-box">
                        <div class="correct">正确答案：$757,505.84</div>
                        <p><strong>解题步骤：</strong></p>
                        <ol>
                            <li>识别变量：PMT = $8,000, r = 7% = 0.07, n = 30</li>
                            <li>选择公式：FV<sub>A</sub> = PMT × [(1 + r)<sup>n</sup> - 1] / r</li>
                            <li>代入计算：FV<sub>A</sub> = 8,000 × [(1 + 0.07)<sup>30</sup> - 1] / 0.07</li>
                            <li>FV<sub>A</sub> = 8,000 × [7.6123 - 1] / 0.07</li>
                            <li>FV<sub>A</sub> = 8,000 × 94.688 = $757,505.84</li>
                        </ol>
                    </div>
                    <div class="pitfall-box">
                        <div class="title">防坑攻略</div>
                        <ul>
                            <li>❌ 不要用单笔终值公式：FV = PV × (1+r)<sup>n</sup></li>
                            <li>✅ 要用年金终值公式，因为这是<strong>定期存款</strong></li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="exercise-box">
                    <h4 style="color: #9c27b0; margin-bottom: 15px;">例题 4：贷款月供计算</h4>
                    <p class="question">你申请了一笔$200,000的房贷，贷款期限20年，年利率6%，每月等额还款。每月需要还款多少钱？（提示：年利率需要转换为月利率，期数转换为月数）</p>
                    <div class="answer-box">
                        <div class="correct">正确答案：$1,432.86</div>
                        <p><strong>解题步骤：</strong></p>
                        <ol>
                            <li>识别变量：PV = $200,000, 年利率 = 6%, 年限 = 20年</li>
                            <li>转换单位：月利率 r = 6%/12 = 0.5% = 0.005, 月数 n = 20×12 = 240</li>
                            <li>使用年金现值公式求PMT：PV<sub>A</sub> = PMT × [1 - (1 + r)<sup>-n</sup>] / r</li>
                            <li>200,000 = PMT × [1 - (1 + 0.005)<sup>-240</sup>] / 0.005</li>
                            <li>200,000 = PMT × [1 - 0.3019] / 0.005</li>
                            <li>200,000 = PMT × 139.58</li>
                            <li>PMT = 200,000 / 139.58 = $1,432.86</li>
                        </ol>
                    </div>
                    <div class="pitfall-box">
                        <div class="title">防坑攻略</div>
                        <ul>
                            <li>❌ 千万不要直接用年利率和年数！</li>
                            <li>✅ 年利率 ÷ 12 = 月利率</li>
                            <li>✅ 年限 × 12 = 总月数</li>
                            <li>✅ 单位必须统一！</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
