                            <td>Takeover Threat</td>
                            <td>收购威胁</td>
                            <td>业绩差的公司可能被收购</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>Managerial Labor Market</td>
                            <td>管理层劳动力市场</td>
                            <td>声誉机制影响职业发展</td>
                        </tr>
                    </table>

                    <div class="note">
                        💡 <strong>核心理解：</strong>股东想的是"公司价值最大化"，管理层想的是"个人利益最大化"，两者不完全一致！
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="subsection">
                    <h3 class="subsection-title">四、财务目标</h3>

                    <div class="concept-box">
                        <div class="english">The primary goal of financial management is to maximize the current value of the firm's stock, or to maximize the market value of the existing owners' equity.</div>
                        <div class="chinese">财务管理的首要目标是<strong>最大化公司股票的当前价值</strong>，或者最大化现有股东权益的市场价值。</div>
                    </div>

                    <table>
                        <tr>
                            <th>英文原文</th>
                            <th>中文解析</th>
                            <th>评价</th>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>Maximize Stock Price</td>
                            <td>最大化股价</td>
                            <td>✅ 最佳目标</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>Maximize Profit</td>
                            <td>最大化利润</td>
                            <td>❌ 忽视风险和时间价值</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>Maximize Sales</td>
                            <td>最大化销售额</td>
                            <td>❌ 忽视成本和利润</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>Maximize Market Share</td>
                            <td>最大化市场份额</td>
                            <td>❌ 可能牺牲利润</td>
                        </tr>
                    </table>

                    <div class="pitfall-box">
                        <div class="title">为什么不是"最大化利润"？</div>
                        <p><strong>English:</strong></p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Profit does not consider the timing of cash flows (TVM)</li>
                            <li>Profit does not consider the risk associated with the earnings</li>
                            <li>Profit can be manipulated through accounting choices</li>
                        </ul>
                        <p><strong>中文:</strong></p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>❌ 利润不考虑现金流的时间价值</li>
                            <li>❌ 利润不考虑收益的风险</li>
                            <li>❌ 利润可以通过会计手段操纵</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
